<div class="block">
  <h2 class="header">DATE &amp; PLACE</h2>
<p>
The GRACE International Meeting will take place at 
<a href="http://www.shonan-village.co.jp/english_index.html">Shanon Village
Center</a>, December 15-18, 2008. Built on a hill commanding a view of
Mt. Fuji and overlooking Sagami Bay, Shonan Village Center offers a
combination of facilities for conferences, training, and lodging in a
resort-like setting.</p>

